ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b49ff125b181d27171ab3f75f3fc14f66e56ab0f","tid":145932,"uid":45650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:10:09.000Z","msg":"屌 邊撚個黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又要溫書睇返之前果D"},{"pid":"22278fef6ff6649002fc66eca681be6f9db16b57","tid":145932,"uid":9024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5010611625?see_lz=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5010611625%3Fsee_lz%3D1&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2zOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b8611051\" target=\"_blank\">https://tieba.baidu.com/p/5010611625?see_lz=1</a><br />\n<br />\n日文全圖生肉"},{"pid":"359e5535bae2e903005eab43072971afc0c39882","tid":145932,"uid":62352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女會唔會係東洋人"},{"pid":"8ef49f77d36f9bb8f11cfd8f20198432376b31c9","tid":145932,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T05:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後一隻巨人登場<br />\n下巴巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上一代凱巨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0450ef7cb398c5aa322e907ec9eb6453621f8e","tid":145932,"uid":9024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後一隻巨人登場<br />\n下巴巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上一代凱巨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX年之後<br />\n<br />\n日文生肉有寫<br />\n<br />\nX自己睇"},{"pid":"90215c9d3c51c8e51253f95a19d1b71809b357e8","tid":145932,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:40:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>最後一隻巨人登場<br />\n下巴巨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上一代凱巨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX年之後<br />\n<br />\n日文生肉有寫<br />\n<br />\nX自己睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n今次呢集, 是 猿巨+鐵甲巨 撤退四年後<br />\n<br />\n馬來國 與 中東聯合國開戰.......<br />\n<br />\n然後係呢場戰爭入面,選出下一任 鐵甲巨人"},{"pid":"13e1eb5b04f7ea6849e4042bade2af29b09b8a41","tid":145932,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:54:41.000Z","msg":"簡單來講<br />\n<br />\n馬來國 打緊兩條戰線, 一條是今集既中東戰線, 一條是艾倫果個島既戰線<br />\n<br />\n中東戰線, 就好似 第一次世界大戰 咁, 兩批士兵互射, 互射開炮 之類<br />\n不過,馬來國帶左 車力巨人和 顎巨人(最後登場果個) ........不過未變身<br />\n因為呢兩隻巨人, 都是速度型, 但防衛力弱<br />\n而敵方既中東國,  一早知道馬來會派巨人參戰, 所以準備左 巨炮火車,<br />\n巨炮火車 就係專門針對巨人而設, 可以瘋狂開炮, 打爆巨人後頸, 殺死巨人<br />\n(車力巨人.......今集無出場, 但懷疑就是果隻 四腳爬爬巨人)<br />\n<br />\n所以今集果個指揮官, 唔敢派巨人參戰, 擔心被消滅<br />\n而且個指揮官仲話:「如果我地攻唔陷個陣地, 就要調實力更強既猿巨人和凱巨人來攻」<br />\n(證明左, 用科技力量, 可以壓制巨人......)<br />\n<br />\n於是個女仔自動衝上去, 用炸彈 炸爆巨炮火車<br />\n然後 顎巨人馬上變身, 打爆敵人既機槍陣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同一時間<br />\n已經選出 下一任猿巨人.........估計 吉斯 已經快死, 所以要選下一任<br />\n而下一任凱巨人, 依然選緊<br />\n<br />\n其中一個鏡頭, 就是萊納 坐係飛機上面., 身邊仲有幾個士兵........估計是準備投入戰場........不過唔知道投入 艾倫果邊既戰場, 定係中東戰線"},{"pid":"2d0bf8bd9375f0bc80dc371edd011f91c6e1bfd7","tid":145932,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:26:13.000Z","msg":"全新故事咁....<br />\n係咪個作者plan 定巨人既故事已到尾聲，依家諗住開新漫畫，索性砌入巨人個故事到增收視..."},{"pid":"2337cc069598837492140dd9f0efaf79f7d65c7a","tid":145932,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:20:32.000Z","msg":"等睇所有巨人合體變成零波麗reset成個世界"},{"pid":"c79f7d79a