<br />\n好似話9年前係試派4個細路去帕拉迪島, 所以計一計應該係上集既4年後?"},{"pid":"4889a283eaf134f8b4c9a39adce19aa020c689d7","tid":145932,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T18:03:11.000Z","msg":"艾倫同米卡沙扑野生仔未"},{"pid":"ecf9607b848fd2e6183c4b79371f5f2bdb28a8c6","tid":145932,"uid":87069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:09:02.000Z","msg":"點解今個月8號都未有中文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n即係個故事突然skip左艾倫登陸打佢地既事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}